snippet.title: The Tomb of Corruption - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
coming soon to gog.com (if they accept me lol) or to itch.io!

The Tomb of Corruption is an action game developed by me for the past year. I'm working hard to get it doon as soon as possible. Please provide any feedback you can. I'll make a free demo version avaliable soon, so you can try it for yourself.
